WEBVTT

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:30.576
I vi ste, također.

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:34.336
To me dovelo do izgradnje lasera
i računala i modelarskih raketa,

00:00:34.360 --> 00:00:37.360
a to me dovelo do izrade
raketnog goriva u mojoj spavaćoj sobi.

00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:41.616
Sad, u znanstvenim terminima,

00:00:41.640 --> 00:00:44.896
to nazivamo vrlo lošom idejom.

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:46.136
(Smijeh)

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:48.336
Nekako oko tog doba,

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:51.576
Kubrick-ova "2001: Odiseja u Svemiru"
je došla u kina,

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.800
i moj se život zauvijek promijenio.

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:56.336
Volio sam sve oko tog filma,

00:00:56.360 --> 00:00:58.896
posebno HAL 9000.

00:00:58.920 --> 00:01:00.976
Sad, HAL je bio svjesno računalo